data.persona: I fly during the day to look for food. I do not like eagles. I sometimes get caught and eaten.
data.description:
You are in the Bog.
Frogs croak in the reeds that surround the bog. The water is very murky and underneath the surface tadpoles dart around. There are minimal places to stand to stay dry.
There's a moss, a reeds, a water, a tree, and a bog here.
The spider and the fish are here.

You are carrying a worm.

data.short_motivation: I need to get pieces of bog in order to build my nest.
data.mid_motivation: I have to gather reeds and algae to construct the walls of my house.
data.long_motivation: I want to build my home out of the bog itself, so it'll be camouflaged from the outside.
